column2: SELECT p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.b, p.l, p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,s.class, s.subclass, s.velDisp,s.z as redshift FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   (p.b between # and #) AND (p.l between # and #)  AND (s.z between # and #)  AND (s.class = &&& OR s.class = &&&)
